---
import { Footer } from "../components/Footer.jsx";
import { Navbar } from "../components/Navbar.jsx";
import { ScrollUpButton } from "../components/ScrollUpButton";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/Diagonals.css";
import "../styles/Theme.css";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Twitch Follower Badge">
  <Navbar client:load />
  <div class="flex w-screen py-12">
    <div
      class="text-white flex flex-col gap-4 p-24 text-justify 2xl:w-[1280px] xl:w-10/12 w-11/12 mx-auto"
    >
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">
        Privacy Policy for <span class="text-twitch">Twitch Follower Badge</span> Chrome Extension
      </h1>

      <p class="italic">Last Updated: 15-02-2025</p>

      <p class="">
        Thank you for using Twitch Follower Badge, a Chrome extension that enables users to see who follows them on Twitch. 
        This Privacy Policy is designed to inform you about the types of information we collect, how we use that
        information, and the measures we take to protect your privacy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">1. Information We Collect</h2>

      <p class="">Twitch Follower Badge collects the following information:</p>

      <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
        <li>
          <strong>Twitch Username:</strong> When you connect to Twitch Follower Badge, we collect your
          Twitch username to check follower relationships.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Authentication Token:</strong> A secure OAuth token from Twitch that allows us to check follower status.
          This token is stored securely and only used to verify follower relationships.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">2. Data Usage</h2>

      <p class="">
        We take privacy seriously, and as such, we ensure the following:
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
        <li>
          <strong>Minimal Data Collection:</strong> We only collect the data necessary to provide the follower badge functionality.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>No Data Storage:</strong> Follower information is fetched in real-time and is not stored on our servers.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">3. Information Sharing</h2>

      <p class="">
        We do not share your personal information with third parties. Your
        Twitch authentication token and follower data are used solely for the operation of the
        extension and are not disclosed to external entities.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">4. Security Measures</h2>

      <p class="">
        We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your
        information, including secure OAuth authentication through Twitch's official API.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">
        5. Updates and Changes to Privacy Policy
      </h2>

      <p class="">
        We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices or
        for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. It is your
        responsibility to review this policy periodically.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">6. Contact Information</h2>

      <p class="">
        If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the
        privacy practices of Twitch Follower Badge, please contact us at <a
          href="mailto:hello@stormix.co"
          class="text-twitch hover:underline"
        >
          hello@stormix.co
        </a>
        .
      </p>

      <p class="">
        By using the Twitch Follower Badge Chrome extension, you agree to the terms outlined in
        this Privacy Policy. Please discontinue use if you do not agree with
        these terms.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Footer />
  <ScrollUpButton client:load />
</Layout>
